OL,3,CHalf a million people miss out on
OL,4,Cchild benefit payment after glitch
OL,6,FAround half a million people have been
OL,7,Faffected by an issue which meant that
OL,8,Fsome child payments did not arrive as
OL,9,Fscheduled.
OL,11,FAround 30% of child benefit payments
OL,12,Fscheduled for Monday were not made `
OL,13,Fequating to around 500,000 people
OL,14,Fbeing affected.
OL,16,FHM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) has
OL,17,Fapologised and said it is working
OL,18,Furgently to resolve the issue.
