OL,3,CHalf a million people miss out on
OL,4,Cchild benefit payment after glitch
OL,6,FAn HMRC spokesperson said: "We're
OL,7,Fsorry that some customers' child
OL,8,Fbenefit payments have not arrived as
OL,9,Fscheduled and we are working urgently
OL,10,Fto resolve the issue.
OL,12,F"The issues that caused payment
OL,13,Fproblems today will not impact
OL,14,Fpayments scheduled for tomorrow."
OL,16,FChild benefit is usually paid every
OL,17,Ffour weeks on a Monday or a Tuesday.
