OL,3,CHalf a million people miss out on
OL,4,Cchild benefit payment after glitch
OL,6,FSome people may receive the benefit
OL,7,Fweekly, for example, if they are a
OL,8,Fsingle parent or receiving certain
OL,9,Fother benefits, such as universal
OL,10,Fcredit.
OL,12,FHMRC also placed a statement on X,
OL,13,Fformerly Twitter, which said: "We're
OL,14,Fsorry that some customers' Child
OL,15,FBenefit payments have not arrived as
OL,16,Fscheduled and we are working urgently
OL,17,Fto resolve the issue.
OL,19,F"There's no need for customers to call
OL,20,Fus and we will provide updates here as
OL,21,Fsoon as they are available."
