OL,3,CHalf a million people miss out on
OL,4,Cchild benefit payment after glitch
OL,6,FAs of August 2023, 6.91 million
OL,7,Ffamilies were in receipt of child
OL,8,Fbenefit payments.
OL,10,FThe weekly child benefit allowance is
OL,11,Fgenerally #25.60 for an eldest or only
OL,12,Fchild and #16.95 per child for
OL,13,Fadditional children.
OL,15,FPeople may be eligible for child
OL,16,Fbenefit if they are responsible for a
OL,17,Fchild under 16 and live in the UK.
OL,19,FThe issue with payments was caused by
OL,20,Fa processing error.
